@group projects
@endpoint GET /projects
@desc Public Projects
@optional {X-Cursor: any # Unique hash used for bypassing the item retrieval limit of 9,000 entities. When using this parameter, please note that the offset parameter will not be available, but the limit parameter will still work as expected., page: any # Page number. Used for pagination with page_size, page_size: any # The number of results included on a page. Used for pagination with page, limit: any # Number of results included on a page. Used for pagination with query, offset: any # Where to start the listing (the offset of the first result). Used for pagination with limit, order: any # The field by which to order. Default varies by endpoint/resource., order_direction: any, institution: any # only return collections from this institution, published_since: any # Filter by article publishing date. Will only return articles published after the date. date(ISO 8601) YYYY-MM-DD, group: any # only return collections from this group}
@returns(200) OK. An array of projects
@errors {400: Bad Request, 422: Bad Request, 500: Internal Server Error}

@endpoint POST /projects/search
@desc Public Projects Search
@optional {X-Cursor: any # Unique hash used for bypassing the item retrieval limit of 9,000 entities. When using this parameter, please note that the offset parameter will not be available, but the limit parameter will still work as expected., search: map # Search Parameters}
@returns(200) OK. An array of projects
@errors {400: Bad Request, 422: Bad Request, 500: Internal Server Error}

